For a feel-good comedy that will have you laughing, **The Wedding Ringer** is a fantastic choice. It's a hilarious tale of a socially awkward groom-to-be who hires a best man to impress his fiancée's family, leading to a series of uproarious mishaps. If you're in the mood for something with a bit of a quirky twist, **3 Idiots** is another gem. It blends humor with heartwarming moments as it follows three friends navigating the ups and downs of college life, all led by the unforgettable character of Rancho. Both movies are sure to lift your spirits and keep you entertained.